koet (1.18.0-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial packaged release.
  * Includes web UI (koet-ui) with Flask backend and IBM Carbon Design System frontend.
  * Added RHEL 9/10 and Rocky Linux 8/9/10 support.
  * Added forward-compatibility for unknown point releases via major-version fallback.
  * Modernized Python stack: dropped Python 2 dead code, uses distro, pathlib, statistics.

